@startuml
!theme plain
title High-Level Architecture - ToyFolio

node "Client Side (Frontend)" {
    component [React App (Vite)] as Client
}

node "Server Side (Backend)" {
    component [Node.js Express Server] as Server
    component [Auth Middleware] as Auth
    component [Catalog Logic] as Logic
}

database "Data Storage" {
    database "MySQL Database" as DB
}

Client <--> Server : JSON / HTTP REST
Server --> Auth : 1. Validate Token/Key
Auth --> Logic : 2. Process Request
Logic <--> DB : 3. Read/Write Data

note right of Client
  User Dashboard
  Admin Panel
  API Playground
end note

note right of Server
  Port: 3000
  Rest API Endpoints
end note

@enduml